    "name": "BlastBall: All-Stars Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3230830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the ultimate sports showdown with <strong>BlastBall: All-Stars!</strong> Pick your favorite all-star from our roster of adorable creatures and jump into the fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/3566728e545d4256cc117869fe97b371.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/094392e615c8a62b09fbb39357ff4e28.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/094392e615c8a62b09fbb39357ff4e28.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/094392e615c8a62b09fbb39357ff4e28.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With intuitive controls adapted to each sport, jumping into new games is a breeze! Aim with the left stick and add spin with the right stick to score <strong>highlight reel goals</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/7cb893d4ea27b46504c62784ba44e7fc.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b3919a8a0636c218ff6ef024c08d39ff.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b3919a8a0636c218ff6ef024c08d39ff.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b3919a8a0636c218ff6ef024c08d39ff.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hitting the ball builds your blast meter, allowing you to unleash powerful blast shots! Need to see that goal again? Then don't skip that replay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/dd07e23784e4e18e947816394ea66c99.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b417c1b74ba70bd3a8d52bdfc46c09b8.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b417c1b74ba70bd3a8d52bdfc46c09b8.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b417c1b74ba70bd3a8d52bdfc46c09b8.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 4 friends</strong> can play Air Hockey, Soccer, Dodgeball, and Volleyball in this <strong>demo</strong>! Need some pickup players? Add a few bots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/ce4305488f639ec11ec2bb9cf6b4a316.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/081628c714305fd9a98e6e48d6ad1265.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/081628c714305fd9a98e6e48d6ad1265.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/081628c714305fd9a98e6e48d6ad1265.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Battle it out in simplified <strong>fan-favorite sports</strong> like soccer, gaga ball, volleyball, and air hockey. Can’t decide what to play first? Compete in a <i>multi-sport tournament</i> to prove who’s the true champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/f7587f2eca01b6bb0c6163b17c5ffb47.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/23bfab857e4496762e39b1882d93357c.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/23bfab857e4496762e39b1882d93357c.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/23bfab857e4496762e39b1882d93357c.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're looking to bend the rules, go right ahead! We have a bunch of options and items to keep your opponents guessing. Giant players, tiny pucks, screwballs, mini bumpers... and many more to come!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/bdf92aba2c7cc755db186256cbf5b49e.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b66c3682f4ab58133a6931ec6b896b07.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b66c3682f4ab58133a6931ec6b896b07.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/b66c3682f4ab58133a6931ec6b896b07.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only have a few minutes to play? Get a match going <i>in less than 30 seconds</i>. We can't help if you don't want to stop, though!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/f6f1577739d4612d98eb153fa924b376.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/14c530b6694f0125995eca2df6bdf405.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/14c530b6694f0125995eca2df6bdf405.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/14c530b6694f0125995eca2df6bdf405.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've got your favorite sports covered (or we're working on it, at least..), and we plan to keep expanding the game with more sports and modes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/4302b9caa4f024dcb8d0161b70360f71.webp?t=1741382946\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/912470cb696f5f76adaa1ed99fa512fc.poster.avif?t=1741382946\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/912470cb696f5f76adaa1ed99fa512fc.webm?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230830/extras/912470cb696f5f76adaa1ed99fa512fc.mp4?t=1741382946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Becca, Reggie, Blaire, and Kazuo are <strong>ready to play</strong> in the demo! Each character brings unique stats and styles to keep players on their toes. Give the<strong> FREE DEMO</strong> a try today! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
